<TEXT>
   An anesthetist burst into an operating
room Friday and shot to death a doctor he suspected of having an
affair with his girlfriend, wounded the woman and then fatally shot
himself, it was reported.
   Despite the shootings, other doctors continued working on young
patient, removing his appendix, the news agency AGI said.
   The anesthetist, Vincenzo Parisi, entered the operating room at
